HEADWORD: Unlink
<hw>Un*link"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>link</ets>.]</ety> <def>To separate or undo, as
links; to uncoil; to unfasten.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
